  "version": "1.0",
  "standard": "STING SEED FAMILY — Fire Damper (BS EN 1366-2, BS EN 15650, NFPA 90A)",
  "_notes": [
    "Fire-damper seed for ducts crossing fire-rated barriers. Ducts",
    "must NOT use a firestop sealant — they need a UL-classified or",
    "BS EN 15650-certified fire damper that closes when its fusible",
    "link or actuator triggers. PenetrationProductSelector dispatches",
    "to this seed when the penetrating member is a duct (round or",
    "rectangular) and the host is a fire-rated wall, slab, or floor."
